data.description: Here's your opportunity to become the new owner of this 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom townhouse in Chambers Knoll. Being sold by the original owners, this home is well loved and maintained. The 2 story foyer leads into open 1st floor with large living room, dining room and kitchen. Upstairs offers primary suite complete with bathroom and walk in closet, 2 additional bedrooms, a 2nd full bath and laundry. The unfinished basement is waiting for your personal touch to transform into whatever you may need!
